係咁吹到人地有幾差，自己有幾好（但叫人有沉穩自信基本上冇咩原因，就係文章前段嗰堆廢話），同時絕口不提自己國家幾差<br />\n<br />\n此為打飛機之極致，中華文化"},{"pid":"30054b6c0e9d7afeea86d4261854e98973766755","tid":1089578,"uid":65194,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2017/3-28/p1532171a770721317-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2017%2F3-28%2Fp1532171a770721317-ss.jpg&h=aa0bf5e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自以為正統 點知連自己都唔尊重自己文化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eebc6f839c11f7466900caac099fbfab41db47a","tid":1089578,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:01:21.000Z","msg":"咁都打飛機"},{"pid":"b2aebd3c972584a662a42b6f0207c1224ef3a1de","tid":1089578,"uid":50310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76d9bbabfc4c551b6c46320c10b09d99c8201c18","tid":1089578,"uid":66324,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T01:57:14.000Z","msg":"日本漢字意思已經同中文唔同，嘈乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:07:14.000Z","msg":"咪係！日文字 和 解 贏！<br />\n你估又 xx或成大贏家<br />\n佢只求和嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1edd9da2c4aa14daebb9df2f1db54643784a230e","tid":1089578,"uid":87428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:12:25.000Z","msg":"日本也是中國的"},{"pid":"011d9ace0078bf4f3e48d27997d9adcac24a4b5f","tid":1089578,"uid":204429,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"0d56004ba4592d8dced6da794958c27f512ccf1f","tid":1089578,"uid":4942,"like":501,"dislike":3,"score":498,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T01:36:06.000Z","msg":"人地係用漢代古字<br />\n<br />\n你睇下你支國用緊乜野字先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"